org.fhnw.aigs.RockPaperScissors.commons

Class RockPaperScissorsResultMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.Message
      • org.fhnw.aigs.RockPaperScissors.commons.RockPaperScissorsResultMessage

  • public class RockPaperScissorsResultMessage
extends org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.Message
    Class used by the server to inform the client of the result of a move. The result is from the point-of-view of the specific client; each client receives a different message.
